Darren Clarke, Dustin Johnson Share British Open Lead at 4 Strokes Under

-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 
2011-07-16T16:07:15Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-16/darren-clarke-takes-one-stroke-lead-at-british-open-after-glover-s-bogey.html
Dustin Johnson  and Darren Clarke are
tied for the lead at 4-under par in the third round of the
British Open.  Johnson is 2-under par through 12 holes today and Clarke,
who shared the overnight lead with Lucas Glover, is even par
through eight holes. Glover and Thomas Bjorn are one shot back
at 3-under and still on the course.  Rickie Fowler shot 2-under-par 68 to reach 2-under, tied
for fifth with Anders Hanson, Chad Campbell and  Davis Love III .
U.S. Open champion Rory McIlroy shot 74 and is 4-over par for
the tournament.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bob Bensch at 
 bbensch@bloomberg.net  